Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.85,0:00:37.79,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.86,0:00:42.69,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an9}となりでいつも 見つめてたい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.76,0:00:46.16,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}覚えててくれるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.23,0:00:51.50,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}幼い約束を
